author: Shelley Ng
title: Photo: Small plane makes emergency landing in Florida Everglades; 2 people on board and no injuries reported - @nbc6
text:
A Cessna makes an emergency landing in the Florida Everglades. Updated at 9:42 AM EDT on Friday, Aug 14, 2015 Authorities responded to a small plane that was forced to land on a dirt road in the Florida Everglades in Parkland Friday morning. Two people were aboard the Cessna when it made the emergency landing, U.S. Coast Guard officials said. The two people were hoisted to safety and no one was injured, officials said. It's unknown what caused the plane to go down. Published at 8:35 AM EDT on Aug 14, 2015
